# Neahttadigis√°nit command cheat sheet:

Command                    What it does
-------------------------------------------------------------
nds update PROJECT         Updates dictionaries sources
                           (pulls from github)
nds compile PROJECT        Compiles dictionary from sources
                           (do this after update)
nds restart PROJECT        Restarts the server for PROJECT
                           (do this after compiling dictionaries)
nds strings extract        Compile translation strings
                           (do this after adding translations)
nds strings compile        Compile .po to .mo (all dictionaries)
                           (do this after adding translations)
nds test PROJECT           Checks configuration and FST files
nds add-stem               Adds stem information to smenob
nds ls                     List projects (baakoeh, sanit, sanat, etc)
                           (use nds ls --help for more info)
nds --help                 Shows commands, general info
nds compile --help         Shows help on "compile" command

The commands are defined in neahtta/nds_commands.py.
